programme.desc: 眾人執拾診所時發現折韁留下的血圖案，卻猜不透其含意。德莉得知成虎打黑拳真相，感動不已。迎風突然贊成讓福利會接管黃賭毒，朝陽反對。朝陽從刁蘭口中知道父死真相，晴天霹靂！朝霞準備了毒酒，刁蘭二話不說喝下。

programme.title: 東張西望[粵]
programme.desc: 美職聯球會與港隊上演表演賽，「球王」美斯全程坐後備席觀賽，令球迷不滿，更高呼「回水」！購票入場的陳庭欣感失望，並稱不少球迷要「報東張」。劉倬昕拍到有人闖球隊下榻酒店情況；體育學者則評論美斯受傷說法。某單位坐廁突然湧出污水，住戶向管理員求助卻遭冷待，法團更指曾出信警告屋內沙井違規被封，無法清理。專業人士上門視察後揭沙井不在該單位內，究竟污水倒灌入屋責任誰屬？脂肪肝原來與腸道健康有關，可如何護腸？

programme.title: 流行都市[粵]
programme.desc: 迎接新春，大家都想為親友準備豐富賀年盛宴，鮑魚、海參、花膠等海味更是不少人的心頭好。專家攜來上述乾貨佳品，介紹挑選貼士與浸發技巧。而乾鮑表面如出現粉狀，更是特別滋味。兔年整體經濟未如理想，蘇民峰師傅預測龍年將向好發展，哪些行業較為興旺？師傅亦以九宮飛星圖，教各位佈置風水家居。有機構就大專學生的投資情況進行研究，項目代表詳析結果。「睇餸食飯」環節，陳國賓用大蝦、南瓜等，炮製意頭菜「壽比南山笑哈哈」。

programme.title: 錦心似玉#28[粵/普]

programme.desc: 方紹聰(奶仔)帶首集嘉賓江嘉敏勇闖東龍島，挑戰懸崖飛索，沿途還會探問她的工作趣事。《親親我好媽》是嘉敏於TVB的首部劇集，她難忘被何廣沛親吻一幕的緊張情形，對着樹幹重演，演技可有猛進？抵達目的地，嘉敏單看教練示範飛索已嚇至腳震？奶仔成功飛越後，輪到嘉敏登場，但擾攘近一小時，她仍未「步出」懸崖！嘉敏另提到入行初時，媽媽曾「潛行睡房」欲了解其拍攝日程，卻不小心摔破擺設，母女頓陷「冷戰」，及後如何收科？

programme.title: 野外步出[粵]
programme.desc: 嘉賓陳庭欣(Toby)熱衷滑水，主持方紹聰(奶仔)縱使對活動經驗欠奉，仍無懼隨她出海挑戰「無繩滑水」Wakesurf。奶仔新手試玩期間，Toby更會化身熱血教練！Toby接着下水大顯身手，不但輕鬆完成花式動作及擺出十連拍甫士，而且在滑水板上接水樽及喝水，展現了香港小姐的優雅一面。她亦會分享當年參選港姐的經過，還自評競選當晚表現幼嫩。回到岸邊，Toby與奶仔靜下對談，深情細訴跟鸚鵡的「愛情」故事。

programme.title: 北歐潮什麼[粵]
programme.desc: 挪威最大的海盜主題樂園，廣受大、小朋友喜愛。芷珮攜眷入場，勇闖迷宮、試玩掘金，還登上海盜船，體驗海上激戰！一家人樂而忘返，索性住進海盜主題酒店，全情投入海盜世界。芷珮及後慕名到訪世界級咖啡店，一試冠軍咖啡師的手藝。西南部城市斯塔萬格，開設了十多個特色博物館。罐頭博物館兼工場，可認識製作沙甸魚罐頭的步驟，並一嚐以傳統方法燻燒的沙甸魚。石油博物館則展示探挖、生產石油的歷史，芷珮了解後更揚言要轉行鑽油！

programme.title: 還原神之食[粵]
programme.desc: 這集繼續力求還原《美味天王》菜式，並參考劇中古天樂製作的「石燒芝士龍蝦」，積奇更指菜餚跟法式名菜「龍蝦米多」相似。欣茵、泳芍仿照劇集情節，做菜前先挑選龍蝦。海鮮達人為她們準備了朱龍、澳洲岩龍、法國藍龍等，並分享揀龍蝦要訣。古天樂於劇內教導徒弟揀選「孖指」龍蝦，原來這確是要領之一？積奇把龍蝦起肉走油，加入法式白醬、芝士烹調，然後放回龍蝦殼入爐焗香。期間欣茵要求加進伊麵，卻被積奇取笑她令菜式降格。

programme.title: 黃金庭院#27[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 東珠要Sabrina歸還用東珠身分搶走的一切，蘭淑阻止。東珠找到身世知道蘭淑非生母，找律師提出訴訟拿回一切。東珠與蘭淑深談不歡而散，Sabrina求東珠別將往事告訴南熙。奶奶和秀美得知部分MS病友的股份被同一人買下。

programme.title: 網紅甜卡[粵]
programme.desc: Christy、Jessica穿上型格「牛仔」便服，尋找隱世名店盡情打卡！古老建築內原是網紅餐廳，共設五個不同風格的用餐區，其中以粉紅色為主調的茶館供食客享用甜品，感覺超夢幻！蘇豪區黃金地段隱藏「人氣」蛋糕店，賣相吸引的紙杯蛋糕大受歡迎，老闆娘「爆紅」原來有段勵志故事？醋廠跳蚤市場可找到不少特色古著，Veronica遇上想法一致的檔主，可有收獲？兩位主持再去紅磚巷市集「掃街」，感受地道文化氣息！

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: Gin Lee愛吃日式火鍋，尚友專誠用貴價海螯蝦製作火鍋料理。藝人常要戒口，Gin卻稱打邊爐「凍食」就無問題？她自揭馬來西亞家園種植菠蘿、蔗等，6號驚訝空間限制想像！以貓屎咖啡做提拉米蘇，滋味昇華。為測Gin打發忌廉功力，搞鬼6號在她頭上倒轉忌廉碗……撒朱古力粉時，她勾起童年回憶，還笑言曾「運粉」來港。該飲品港版、大馬版試味挑戰，她竟飲到發脾氣？回望在港發展辛酸，她為慳錢不出街，更差點放棄歌手夢？

programme.title: 開卷[粵]
programme.desc: 主持們這次到訪的書店位於基隆港附近，店內很多東西都含有海洋的元素，樓上還提供享用咖啡與休憩的空間，韻婷更即席玩手鼓自娛！書店老闆在海邊居住，曾從事跟海洋有關的工作，由他推介的讀物有何特別？自由潛愛好者泳芍揀來以「幻想」視角窺探深海之書，卻發覺自己對海洋的熟知度不足！由日本心理學家撰寫的書籍，採用漫畫形式將職場的心理學表達出來。隨着故事發展，讀者還可學習怎樣於初見面予人良好印象，甚或一些戀愛技巧。

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#11[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 故事講述一名背叛了丈夫和生病的兒子，為了愛情和慾望拋家棄子的母親，與懷著對母親怨恨的女兒多年後再次見面，並開始對自己母親展開復仇計畫。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 本應是愉快的韓國之旅，期間一次意外卻令歌手迪子跌進人生低谷。迪子在咖啡店內絆倒，面部撞向鋼椅，導致牙齒、嘴部嚴重受創，出事後更要大幅度縫針。除了親述這段觸目驚心的受傷經過，迪子又提到當時囑咐朋友為她隱瞞家人，何以有此想法？迪子性格樂觀，還拿嘴部的傷口自嘲，笑言化身日漫角色！她亦不忘拍照紀錄傷勢，但起初原因竟是為了求救？迪子及後進行牙齒修復之外，也要接受整容療程，且聽她細訴臉上部位的調整情況。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 意外帶來的不一定只有負面挫折，女歌手迪子受傷破相，經歷反讓她較前更有自信。她還將箇中體會融入音樂作品，唱出普遍人口說不介意別人外貌，實際卻是另一回事。迪子意外後要接受整容治療，更自拍歷程製作MV。手術醒來一刻，竟還不忘拍攝！她亦揭開整容的神秘一面，例如手術後要坐着睡覺的原因。歌曲以綑綁帶出愛情關係，迪子又認為每段戀愛總有「S」與「M」，何出此言？她數年前毅然與唱片公司「分手」，又是為了甚麼緣故？

programme.title: 姊妹淘[粵]
programme.desc: 今次接受大改造的Tim是一個二十四歲的大男孩，他的外表忠厚老實，衣著也較為平實。他希望藉著今次機會學習穿搭技巧，擺脫過往較為老套的形象，來個華麗大變身。為了增加他的內在，《姊妹淘》帶他去學習魔術。魔術易學難精，要流暢地作出整個魔術表演殊不簡單。Tim不斷認真嘗試，務求能在日後派上用場。今集以形象指導Miu、星級化妝師Kenneth及星級髮型師Roy為變身兵團班底，首先由髮型師Roy為Tim踏出第一步。他把Tim的頭髮修剪得更短，之後再替頭髮弄出造型，令Tim不再「薯嘜」。

programme.title: 開端#12[粵/普][PG]
programme.desc: 遊戲架構師肖鶴雲和女大學生李詩情在公交車爆炸的交通事故後「死而復生」，陷入時間循環。他們於密閉空間自救、努力阻止爆炸，並尋找出兇手才能結束循環。

programme.title: 日常生活搶知識[粵/日]
programme.desc: 世界上充滿了古老的民間傳說、神秘的都市傳聞和有趣的故事，來做個驗證找出答案！

programme.title: 街頭少女戰士[粵/韓]
programme.desc: One Team Performance任務繼續進行，每組都使出渾身解數。綜合導師評分和大眾評分後，最高分的四組可以全員留下，而最低分的四組要進行兩個回合的組內淘汰Battle，由導師決定哪隊能留下…

programme.title: MUSIC BREAK[粵]
programme.desc: 本集由劉詠彤Angel(@angelauwt)推介歌單，播放的MV包括薛家燕、茜拉Shila《有有有Year of the Yo!》；「勁歌金榜No.1」吳業坤《分手前中後》、陳明憙《Little Love》；張學友、鄭秀文《恭喜你》；任賢齊、農夫《紅包拿來》；Twins《你最紅》；太極、蔡立兒、陳德彰、林姍姍、周啟生、曾航生、劉錫明《祝福你》；容祖兒、林峯《喜氣洋洋2010》。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 七十至九十年代香港樂壇巨星輩出，背後有賴一班幕後音樂人的強勁支援，其中一位是殿堂級音樂導師Albert。Albert從小接觸西方樂隊音樂，七歲開始學習結他，長大後成為結他導師；及後自立門戶，創辦教Band課程，詳情如何？當年的樂器價格不菲，學生則主要為興趣而學習音樂，跟現時有甚麼大不同？Albert門生眾多，已故的Beyond主音黃家駒亦是其中之一；談到家駒中學時期登門學電結他，有何深刻點滴？

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 資深音樂導師Albert Sir在七十年代投身流行音樂教育領域，九十年代轉為編寫教學課程，及後與時並進，研發電子課程，見證着香港樂壇的興衰！他如何看時下樂壇的發展？卡拉OK的出現對樂壇發展有利有弊，Albert認為這種娛樂無疑能帶起歌唱風氣，但同時令歌手的整體水準拉低，有甚麼獨到見解？Albert當年於本地樂壇盛世推出歌書，輯錄大熱歌曲的樂譜，備受歡迎。他細說出書緣由，及怎樣迎合市場作出相應調整。

programme.title: 北歐潮什麼[粵]
programme.desc: 丹麥之旅第一站，芷珮帶小朋友走進夢寐以求的積木主題樂園，玩足一日！積木車駕駛體驗是小孩必玩項目；多個用積木砌成的迷你景點，更是不可錯過的打卡位。芷珮及後踏上藝術博物館頂層的彩虹環形通道，透過七彩玻璃觀賞市內風光。另一間開放式露天博物館，設置各式懷舊設施，芷珮入場感受復古氣息，試玩消防車水喉、品嚐地道小吃。哥本哈根工廠區內藏着一個美食市場，價錢親民之餘，多間「貨櫃店」雲集世界各地美食，讓人大飽口福。

programme.title: 還原神之食[粵]
programme.desc: TVB另一部飲食劇集《食為奴》內，康熙對民間鹹魚包一試難忘。主持們為了還原這款美味包點，前往流浮山向專家請教在港有售鹹魚的種類與特性，聽罷積奇卻提出放棄挑戰……幸好，欣茵、泳芍找到當年為劇集創作鹹魚包的大廚顧問尹達剛，終可「神還原」烹製過程。不過，在尹大師指導的搓皮步驟中，有人成為豬隊友？積奇縱抗拒中式鹹魚，但從西式食材覓得替代，還自創「積奇鹹魚包」！而積奇所用的重味鯷魚，竟暗藏於一支疑似牙膏內？

programme.desc: 東珠要Sabrina歸還用東珠身分搶走的一切，蘭淑阻止。東珠找到身世知道蘭淑非生母，找律師提出訴訟拿回一切。東珠與蘭淑深談不歡而散，Sabrina求東珠別將往事告訴南熙。奶奶和秀美得知部分MS病友的股份被同一人買下。

programme.title: 黃金庭院#28[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 必勝終查明蘭淑霸佔東珠身分是為了公司股份，只要找到正守和東珠的合照就能恢復東珠的身分。Sabrina為重返崔家向媒體透露自己懷孕一事，南熙大怒。俊基意外得知盛旭還活著，蘭淑再度謊稱Sabrina不知情。

programme.title: 網紅甜卡[粵]
programme.desc: Christy、Jessica轉赴「音樂之都」維也納，探索其甜品的歷史淵源。古往今來不少名人曾到訪的地標五星級酒店，大堂、酒吧、套房均瑰麗堂皇，猶如皇宮！二人品嚐酒店的招牌巧克力蛋糕，細味流傳200多年的歷史故事……主打純素甜品的「人氣」咖啡店，牛角包不含蛋奶食材，如何提升美味？其新月外形，原來「有段古」？Veronica又引領主持拜師學造手工帽，加熱、塑形、烤焗等工序新奇有趣，盡顯工匠精湛手藝！

programme.title: 娛樂新聞報道
programme.desc: 每晚緊貼香港娛樂圈的消息，以至世界各地的影視娛樂新聞，報道藝人最新動態、劇集和電影宣傳、演唱會精華、頒獎禮盛況等，甚至遠赴外地採訪娛樂盛事、追蹤各地影星，專訪觀眾熟悉的歌、影、視紅人，讓大家瞬間掌握影視娛樂圈的動態和最新消息。

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: 婆婆弄的撈麵帶給嘉賓糖妹無窮回憶，尚友以日本黑豚肉放入焗爐慢慢烤成叉燒，撈麵上的叉燒醬也是自行調製，再配蔥油享用，怎會不滋味？不過，糖妹亦揭出婆婆撈麵的美味秘密！澳洲芒果、日本純米清酒、香港奶茶，尚友將三地優質飲食結合為港式甜品「奶茶清酒沙巴翁奶凍」。烹調甜品過程中，糖妹講述樂團名字的由來，是希望製造錯摸話題。6號稱糖妹為圈中小富婆，閒談期間，卻發現其致富之道並非做生意，而是買黃金！

programme.title: 關注關注組[粵]
programme.desc: 提到滷味，台式、潮式、港式都是香港人愛吃的口味，而且每間店各有自家的滷水配方，成為吸引顧客的秘訣。「日行」這次穿梭深水埗、旺角、九龍灣三地，試吃生腸、雞腎、墨魚等港式滷味食物，兩人一致認同旺角人龍店的出品最滋味。焯日回到大本營，拍檔們都好奇他外出試食時，稱生腸「有腸味」是甚麼意思？焯日還準備了台式、港式與潮式滷味食品，「大食會」上，十郎與黃嘉雯均「被迫」人生首次試吃生腸，二人又可會喜歡？

programme.title: 北歐潮什麼[粵]
programme.desc: 丹麥之旅第一站，芷珮帶小朋友走進夢寐以求的積木主題樂園，玩足一日！積木車駕駛體驗是小孩必玩項目；多個用積木砌成的迷你景點，更是不可錯過的打卡位。芷珮及後踏上藝術博物館頂層的彩虹環形通道，透過七彩玻璃觀賞市內風光。另一間開放式露天博物館，設置各式懷舊設施，芷珮入場感受復古氣息，試玩消防車水喉、品嚐地道小吃。哥本哈根工廠區內藏着一個美食市場，價錢親民之餘，多間「貨櫃店」雲集世界各地美食，讓人大飽口福。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 七十至九十年代香港樂壇巨星輩出，背後有賴一班幕後音樂人的強勁支援，其中一位是殿堂級音樂導師Albert。Albert從小接觸西方樂隊音樂，七歲開始學習結他，長大後成為結他導師；及後自立門戶，創辦教Band課程，詳情如何？當年的樂器價格不菲，學生則主要為興趣而學習音樂，跟現時有甚麼大不同？Albert門生眾多，已故的Beyond主音黃家駒亦是其中之一；談到家駒中學時期登門學電結他，有何深刻點滴？

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 資深音樂導師Albert Sir在七十年代投身流行音樂教育領域，九十年代轉為編寫教學課程，及後與時並進，研發電子課程，見證着香港樂壇的興衰！他如何看時下樂壇的發展？卡拉OK的出現對樂壇發展有利有弊，Albert認為這種娛樂無疑能帶起歌唱風氣，但同時令歌手的整體水準拉低，有甚麼獨到見解？Albert當年於本地樂壇盛世推出歌書，輯錄大熱歌曲的樂譜，備受歡迎。他細說出書緣由，及怎樣迎合市場作出相應調整。

programme.title: Military and War - The Frontline Grind
programme.desc: The 'Crimea' Battalion fighters came from all works of life. What unites them is that they all left the the comfort of their homes to protect their land and those they love. In 2014, they had to take up arms and learn to fight against the Ukrainian nationalists. Lacking military experience, the soldiers learned and carved out their skills from fighting with the enemy. How have their lives changed over these 9 years?

programme.title: Environment - Arctic Calling
programme.desc: ‘Although our efforts may seem ridiculous and insignificant, the theory of small deeds has to work, we’ve got to fix our planet’, says Vladimir Privalov, ‘Clean Arctic’ volunteer. Vladimir joined the expedition and went to Franz Josef Land to remove car batteries and barrels contaminating the soil and water. Volunteers have to carry out extensive work as previously advanced Arctic research facilities eventually became abandoned and polluted.

programme.title: Arts and Culture - Universal Dostoevsky
programme.desc: Fyodor Dostoevsky is the most recognised Russian writer and can be easily considered a global brand. His novels, released two centuries ago, are still on point and remain the best soul-searching resource for many people around the world. Dostoevsky’s fans discover their true selves while reading him and artists channel their love for the writer through paintings and music. What makes Dostoevsky’s writing immortal?

programme.title: Professions - War Correspondents
programme.desc: In the spring of 2022, Pavel Kukushkin volunteered to travel to Donbass as he sought unbiased assessments of the unfolding events. “Many reporters come, film a report, and leave as fast as they can. I have a different approach. I live with the soldiers, and I need to understand and experience the same feelings they have… when they’re here, so I can report on it more truthfully,” says Kukushkin. Now he helps to defend the people of Donbass with his own weapon – a camera and an opportunity to tell the world what’s really going on.

programme.title: Meeting with Nature - When an Elephant Smiles
programme.desc: Every day, dozens of elephants are killed by poachers seeking for their ivory, meat and other body parts. Elephant calves left without their mothers are sure to die as they lack survival skills and source of food. In Zimbabwe, there is a place where orphaned baby elephants can have a second chance at life. The Zimbabwe Elephant Nursery founded by Roxy Danckwerts on her family farm rescues helpless infants, providing them with care and love 24/7 in a bid to reintegrate mighty animals back to the wild.

programme.title: History - Death Factories
programme.desc: The terrible crimes of Japan's secret Unit 731 make anyone's blood run cold. Thousands of people were used as test subjects for the development of biological weapons. The subjects were injected with cholera, typhoid, anthrax, bubonic plague, to be later dissected alive. The unit's ideologist Shiro Ishii and most of his associates were never punished. They became practising physicians or scientists. Watch our film to find out why.

programme.title: Lifestyle - Philadelphia - Addicted to Freedom
programme.desc: In 2023, homelessness surged again in Philadelphia, marking a three- year increase, as per the annual survey. Homelessness affects people from all walks of life, stripping them of dignity and safety. Many turn to crime out of desperation. Entire neighbourhoods are deserted, while the homeless blatantly inject drugs in broad daylight on trash-ridden streets.

programme.title: Professions - Men of Salt
programme.desc: Salar de Uyuni, the world’s largest salt flat, has been the source of livelihood for generations. Though working on a salt flat can be bad for their health, they still stay, go to work every day and use the salt to build houses and make art pieces. So how does it feel when salt is your whole life?

programme.title: Travel and Adventure - Russian Roots, Mongolian Life
programme.desc: Elena сame to Mongolia for a short business trip and never left. Her daughter now studies Mongolian and attends local children’s clubs. Like many others who relocate, Elena’s family observe both Russian and Mongolian customs and traditions. What attracts people to this ancient land of nomads, camels and enchanting nature?

programme.title: Lifestyle - The Good, The Bad and the Loco
programme.desc: These ladies put on bright bouffant skirts and arrange their long hair in neat plaits. Then they go into the ring and beat the hell out of each other! Meet the Bolivian fighting cholitas, the female wrestlers of lucha libre, a free fight that marries a choreographed show with a full-on punching match.

programme.title: Adopting A New Life Series - Getting to know you - Adopting a new life Ep.1
programme.desc: We meet Stas and Masha, an ordinary Russian couple who have taken on the extraordinary task of adopting six children from troubled backgrounds. The children have become the couple’s world and each has a particular place in their heart. It’s summer time and the family is at their dacha, where all the children get stuck into cleaning up the garden so they can put up the paddling pool.

programme.title: Environment - H2WOE
programme.desc: The Indian state of Punjab is undergoing a severe water crisis. Once an agricultural leader in India, it’s now turning into a desert. Farmers and other rural dwellers are going bankrupt over the need to pay for water delivered from other regions. In this drastic situation, the number of suicides has skyrocketed.

programme.title: Arts and Culture - Art of Gold
programme.desc: Few places in the world still teach fine arts the old way, where form is everything, but the St-Petersburg academy of fine arts is one of them. It’s the oldest art school in Russia and students from all over the world dream of studying within its ancient walls, they believe it’s a place that sets the gold standard in teaching classic art.

programme.title: Discovering Russia - Iceline. Lifeline
programme.desc: In 2022 two brand-new Russian icebreakers will operate on the Northern sea route. These ships can break through ice 118 inches thick, need no refuelling for decades, and travel at sea and along rivers. They opened a new era of Arctic sea economy — now there is a direct path between Northern Europe and Asia, bypassing all European seaports. What new opportunities can it bring?

programme.title: Military and War - Middle East: Vicious Circle of Violence
programme.desc: In our new documentary delving into the historical roots of the Israel-Palestine conflict and the poignant stories from both sides, examine the ongoing crisis in the Middle East. What sparked the Hamas movement? How did they succeed in attacking the Gaza Strip, despite being closely watched by Israeli satellites? What are those factors triggering the endless cycle of violence and prolonged war?

programme.title: History - Spyfall
programme.desc: A mysterious film found in a Moscow flat sheds light on the forgotten spy games in Syria back in the 1960s. At the time the country was almost torn apart by the Western and Soviet intelligence activities.

programme.title: Notes from an american in donbass

Superficially the area appears quiet and steeped in quaint Latin charm, but it proved to be one of the most dangerous places an RTD crew has ever filmed.
